    "en": {
      "title": "Canker sores on penis: 'like being on fire'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As of July 2022, more than 15,000 people worldwide have been diagnosed with measles, according to the World Health Organization (WHO) and the US Centers for Disease Control (CDC).",
        "Monkey disease experts met on Thursday to discuss whether the World Health Organization should classify it as a global health emergency. Following this, the World Health Organization has declared monkeypox as a public health emergency.",
        "Thiago, a Brazilian living in S\u00e3o Paulo, learned he was one of those infected with monkeypox after he went to a local hospital with symptoms including high fever, fatigue, chills and sores all over his body.",
        "But his main problem is pain, swelling and burning sensation in his penile area. At least nine skin lesions appeared on that organ.",
        "\"It's very painful; itchy,\" he said. \"All parts are very swollen. Sometimes it looks like it's on fire.\"",
        "Monkeypox is also caused by the same virus that causes smallpox, but smallpox is much less serious. It is transmitted to humans from an infected animal such as a monkey, rat or squirrel.",
        "Human-to-human transmission is less likely. But it can happen when someone is in close contact with an infected person.",
        "The infection spreads through skin incisions, respiratory tract, eyes and mouth.",
        "The disease can also be spread by touching clothing, bedding or towels used by a person who has rabies."
      ],
